@startuml REQ-0010_Temperature_Sensing
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "User" as User
entity "Mobile" as Mobile

box "IoT Library" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
  participant "Controller" as Controller
end box

header
  **REQ-0010: Temperature Sensing**
  //Description:// Read raw temperature values from the ADC hardware interface\nand post sensor data events for downstream processing.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Sensor_ReadTemperature returns valid ADC reading.\nEVENT_SENSOR_DATA_READY posted with raw value.
end header


== Sensor_ReadTemperature() ==
Sensor_Driver --> Controller: EVENT_SENSOR_DATA_READY

@enduml